\Subject { Purpose:\\ The purpose of this thesis is to study how congested clique algorithms perform on modern supercomputers.\\ Methodology:\\ Studied how an MST algorithm performs on the Puhti supercomputer. The congested clique setting is simulated with MPI\_and CUDA.\\ Result:\\ }
\Keywords {Distributed computing, Supercomputing, Congested clique, MST, Puhti, MPI, CUDA, MPC}
